{"type": "article", "id": 51056, "title": "杜蕾斯开了家 AiR 爱情薄物馆，肯德基的常州新店很粉嫩  | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-03-13T04:39:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 11022, "name": "H5"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 89, "image": "img/article/article_show/201803131210412V5sIhKUdqLBlo0j.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/03/13/johnny-depp-asahi-beer-commercial/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日本朝日啤酒（Asahi beer）最新广告</b></a>，强尼·德普（Johnny Depp）化身摇滚吉他手，在黑暗工厂里秀琴技。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c06048r8axi&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26107.html\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>潘粤明给 Schick 舒适剃须刀拍广告</b></a>，洞察是比较传统的：如何从莽撞男孩蜕变为聪明男人。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=e05663uz03p&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/03/12/the-2018-tvc-of-dazzle-by-zhoudongyu/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>DAZZLE 发布 2018 春夏大片</b></a>，以品牌代言人周冬雨的名字为中心，设定了事事周到、怦然心冬以及雨众不同三个场景。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=l06005c0hfw&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26127.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雷克萨斯台湾发布年度微电影《影藏》</b></a>，由金钟影帝李李仁和夏靖庭出演一对父子。故事刻画父子之间深厚却矛盾的情感，点出父亲肩负着家庭的责任与重担，在工作与家人间两难的迂回情感。全片长达 16 分钟，是台湾影片一贯的细腻和温情。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMzMwMzk1NTkxNg==\" frameborder=\"0\" 'allowfullscreen'=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/44182.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基在常州重装开业了新北万达金街店</b></a>。新店采取自助点餐的模式，鼓励消费者使用肯德基微信公众号或者肯德基 APP 下单。硬件设施改善后，肯德基餐品的价格也随之涨价，但店内并没有推出什么新口味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180313115423NUqWFysEYVbxjKm0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592424\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180313115508l4JSxr1VZOz5dce2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.434848\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018031311551938ZlvUJyVDSP6Hcu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26195.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">杜蕾斯开了家&nbsp;AiR 爱情薄物馆，</a></b>采用了线上 H5 虚拟馆+线下巡展的形式，呈现“爱的厚度，可以很薄”的主题<b>。</b><a href=\"http://durex.buyansu.com/3d/?from=5\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里查看 H5 虚拟馆。</a><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180313115914oPgZk4CMqzFDTdy1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/44225.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>正值职场人的“金三银四”之际</b></a>，职场实名社交平台脉脉做了组马赛克海报。代理公司是&nbsp;MadMonkey。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180313120159uvPCoHOG09xlzkjt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667917\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018031312023868VRFeq35EJmfxba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667292\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：KFC</p>"}